name: Apprehension
description:
While driving home from picking up our new dog, 'Monty', I looked down at him on the front passenger 
seat and he threw me this look! I was feeling a little guilty, as not just 10 mins ago he 
nursed with his mother for that last time. Then it dawned on he, he has no idea what is happening. 
Neither of us realized then, but that was the start of one of the greatest friendships of our lives.
